Russia requested the call, according to The New York Times. Per the White House, Putin and Biden spoke for about 50 minutes. The US Air Force flew two reconnaissance missions over eastern Ukraine this week, the first on December 27 just a few days after Russia said it would withdraw 10,000 troops from the shared border, CNN reported.

- Ukraine has been a point of contention for the two countries since the annexation of Crimea in 2014, Al Jazeera reports

The US Air Force flew two reconnaissance missions over eastern Ukraine this week, the first on December 27 just a few days after Russia said it would withdraw 10,000 troops from the shared border, CNN reported.

- Ukraine has been a point of contention for the two countries since the annexation of Crimea in 2014, Al Jazeera reports
